# Anchor to repo root: the setuptools MANIFEST artifact only appears at the package root.
# Unanchored `MANIFEST` also matched nested `manifest/` dirs (Windows Git is case-insensitive),
# which wrongly ignored the Next.js route app/api/strategies/[strategyId]/manifest/. Fixed 2026-07-03.
/MANIFEST
*.pyc

